            (path 'mixed.csv').write_text 'a,b,c\nd,e,f\r1,2,3'
            File.read (path 'mixed.csv') (Delimited "," headers=True value_formatter=Nothing) Problem_Behavior.Report_Error . should_fail_with Invalid_Row

